| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0440 — Recovery Inhibition (meow)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: dbb1c9c6-d6f3-53b9-9754-5e950ff1b18f"
